short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sets User Agent to allow workintexas.com to work with Chrome OS

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sets the User-Agent string to Chrome running on Windows 10.  It is used for only one website that we need our users to be able to access.  We are using chrome boxes and need to enforce this for our managed guest sessions.  This website blocks any requests using User-Agent string that is not Chrome running on Windows 10.
